# Baseline UI Workflow Validation

- Validate each user-facing slice with browser automation before considering it done.
- Prefer Playwright with `frontend/playwright.config.ts`.
- Use local checks for implementation feedback and deployed checks for integration/cors/auth confidence.
- Keep runtime deterministic on port `3000` when using local validation.
- Report pass/fail outcomes with user-visible evidence.
